title: RHOM: Girl Walks Into a Barf - Live from Orlando
description:
The Real Housewives of Miami trip to the Hamptons culminates in Julia barfing her way through a mystery illness (a hangover) and Larsa overseeing a massively influential brand summit with 25 people. It's high drama.
